{"tid":229492,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日食左個中伏雞煲","createTime":"2017-05-04T15:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T07:16:24.000Z","uid":2221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb6109e756c0357c2c83b0658ed6a994264f5e2","tid":229492,"uid":2221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說小弟今晚去了天水圍天慈邨新開的酒樓金X香試下，點知中伏了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫了小辣雞煲，點知來了勁多辣椒的雞，<br />\n我問部長點解咁辣，佢話D雞全部一齊煮的，<br />\n全部一種辣，咁就唔好寫明分大中小辣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n到叫生料時(見圖X是沒有的)，剔了3次先送來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n點了十樣來得六樣，而食物質數很差，炸魚皮不脆，<br />\n肥牛很肥，還發毛的，生菜爛的，貢丸難食，<br />\n象拔蚌片腥的，服務全無，還有待應送來的雞將隻手指插了入碗內，呢間酒樓不用再去。如果有勇氣既巴打，<br />\n可以去試下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點菜紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7c064X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7c064X.jpg&h=f3c6deeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發霉的肥牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/233226_6cfe30a6af9f57ac5e6c46da6e27d2f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F233226_6cfe30a6af9f57ac5e6c46da6e27d2f6.jpg&h=80cdc14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爛既生菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g23UO54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg23UO54.jpg&h=bb45d8f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得一隻辣既雞煲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/233616_62b9fd4e243b4608e9d526be52acb953.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F233616_62b9fd4e243b4608e9d526be52acb953.jpg&h=bc98af15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n信不信由你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768cbd9bcf0bbb4aa61c5e1a28a04e95399c24e9","tid":229492,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d520e25d5f235c9c3b892f9ff7da2b1842d54834","tid":229492,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"d雞唔熱既咩"},{"pid":"a01329e74081ca50113b5c8d38bedeab2490be85","tid":229492,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d979b8da6a4bcb057906235c3da5aa455b3d137b","tid":229492,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"重點係：幾錢？"},{"pid":"b0d04faa51f2a5a43d16e90c5636c8a9e076e53a","tid":229492,"uid":12957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59624f4ece8eaa362031ffee1970746e9bbf35a7","tid":229492,"uid":2221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重點係：幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7G07136.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7G07136.jpg&h=9d0cea2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e88a7c4c6b67fb20ccca8c5c3f92a4d639199a0","tid":229492,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25c096016453ee3c425b404b03645635732f98e","tid":229492,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-0